comments: Huerter (SAC) makes contact to Edwards' (MIN) head, affecting his shot attempt at the basket.
Edwards (SAC) places a forearm against Anderson (MIN) as the defensive switch occurs and the contact is marginal.
Sabonis (SAC) briefly grabs McDaniels (MIN), who is already off-balance, during the rebound and immediately releases.

Replay review of the foul called on Edwards (MIN) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful.  Edwards contests and initiates contact to Fox's (SAC) wrist that affects the jump shot attempt.
Fox (SAC) commits a take foul on Conley (MIN).
Conley (MIN) legally contests the jump shot attempt by Fox (SAC).
